  • Classes in suncertify.business used by suncertify.business 
    Class and Description
    DefaultSubcontractorService
    DefaultSubcontractorService is the local business service implementation of SubcontractorService.
    RemoteSubcontractorService
    DefaultSubcontractorService is the remote business service implementation of SubcontractorService.
    ServicesException
    ServicesException is the superclass of all exceptions in the suncertify.business package and unless sub-classed can be used to represent a generic exception that has occurred in the business layer
    SubcontractorAlreadyBookedException
    The class SubcontractorAlreadyBookedException should be used when a Subcontractor is not able to be booked on the server if it is already booked by another client
    SubcontractorNotFoundException
    The class SubcontractorNotFoundException should be used to wrap RecordNotFoundException when a subcontractor record is not found.
    SubcontractorService
    The SubcontractorService interface contains the business functionality of the application.
